provenance:
  derived_from:
    - "https://docs.python.org/3/library/asyncio-stream.html — Python asyncio streams documentation"
    - "Test vectors verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-11"
  not_derived_from:
    - "CPython source: Lib/asyncio/streams.py"
  notes:
    - "This spec covers: asyncio.StreamReader and StreamWriter class identity — asyncio.StreamReader.__name__=='StreamReader' (len=12); asyncio.StreamReader.__module__=='asyncio.streams'; asyncio.StreamReader.__mro__.__len__()==2 (StreamReader > object); asyncio.StreamWriter.__name__=='StreamWriter' (len=12; same as StreamReader); asyncio.StreamWriter.__module__=='asyncio.streams' (same module); asyncio.StreamWriter.__mro__.__len__()==2; asyncio.open_connection.__name__=='open_connection' (len=15); asyncio.start_server.__name__=='start_server' (len=12; same as StreamReader)."
    - "asyncio.StreamReader.__name__ == 'StreamReader' (len=12: S-t-r-e-a-m-R-e-a-d-e-r). asyncio.StreamWriter.__name__ == 'StreamWriter' (len=12: S-t-r-e-a-m-W-r-i-t-e-r). Both class names share the same length of 12. Verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-11."
    - "asyncio.StreamReader.__module__ == 'asyncio.streams'. asyncio.StreamWriter.__module__ == 'asyncio.streams'. Both classes are defined in the asyncio.streams submodule. Verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-11."
    - "asyncio.StreamReader.__mro__.__len__() == 2 — MRO is [StreamReader, object]. asyncio.StreamWriter.__mro__.__len__() == 2 — MRO is [StreamWriter, object]. Both are direct subclasses of object. Verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-11."
    - "asyncio.open_connection.__name__ == 'open_connection' (len=15: o-p-e-n-_-c-o-n-n-e-c-t-i-o-n=15). asyncio.start_server.__name__ == 'start_server' (len=12; same as StreamReader). These are the top-level coroutine functions for establishing stream connections. Verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-11."
    - "All expected values verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-11."
  created_at: "2026-04-11T00:00:00Z"

error_model: python_exceptions

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Table 1: asyncio.StreamReader class identity — __name__ and __name__ length
